{"tid":1458343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要間接對大眾市民做成不便","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:56:32.000Z","uid":262346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb42ace308f331aab4336c302c67d955d6ab430","tid":1458343,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"過往不合作運動無錯係make 到noise<br />\n但係做完之後<br />\n所謂中立派會覺得運動搞鳩到自己搵食<br />\n因為直接阻到反工<br />\n<br />\n而政府之所以做左咁多仆街野<br />\n大把港豬都唔屌<br />\n仲覺得冇野<br />\n係因為冇直接影響到佢<br />\n實情係由納稅人埋單<br />\n<br />\n所以不合作運動<br />\n可以影其他普羅市民既需要<br />\n如阻住貨運供應鏈<br />\n發夢佔領高鐵貨運列車<br />\n發夢打爆地產霸權玻璃等<br />\n<br />\n甚至利民既野<br />\n發夢夢見打爆咪錶<br />\n發夢打爆狗鐵部閘機<br />\n<br />\n就算今次點解佔領機場唔會影響民意<br />\n係因為影響到去旅行既人only<br />\n<br />\n唔會直接影響市民生計既野<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb9762e640d06a9ea93ca3b7bedb68907169021","tid":1458343,"uid":265171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:51.000Z","msg":"高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆店鋪玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎佔機場真係做得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, blocked"},{"pid":"b93ba8d8707c842b840925a2e0eb8cd3bad6efb0","tid":1458343,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}